1947;;T-Men;;American;;Anthony Mann;;Dennis O'Keefe;;film noir;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/T-Men;;The story involved two U.S. Treasury ("T-men") agents who go undercover in Detroit and then Los Angeles in an attempt to break a U.S. currency counterfeiting ring.<br><br>The agents try to join the gang by posing as counterfeiters from out of town. They eventually join the gang but the stakes are set even higher when one of the agents is killed by the gang while the other undercover T-man watches in horror.